    func solution(_ phone_number:String) -> String {
    var arr: [String] = []
    var num: String = "" 
    
    if phone_number.count >= 4 && phone_number.count <= 20 {
        for i in phone_number {
            arr.append(String(i))
        }        
        if arr.count > 4 { 
            for i in 0...arr.count - 1 {
                if i < arr.count - 4 {
                    num += "*"
                } else {
                    num += arr[i]
                }
            }
        } else {
            num = phone_number
        }
    }    
    return num
}
